# AVPlayerInterstitialEvent.TimelineOccupancy.fill

**Case**

The event fills the integrated timeline with the duration of this event.

## Declaration

```swift
case fill
```

## Values

- **AVPlayerInterstitialEvent.TimelineOccupancy.singlePoint**: The event occupies a single point on the integrated timeline.
